                    for picture in aboutPictureNumbers
                        div(class="about_picture_box_mobile about_picture_mobile_box_" + picture)
                            picture.about_picture_mobile
                                source(media="(max-width: 750px)", srcset="../img/picture-" + picture + "-sml.jpg")
                                source(media="(min-width: 751px)", srcset="../img/picture-" + picture + "-lrg.jpg")
                                img.about_picture_img_mobile(src="../img/picture-" + picture + "-sml.jg", alt="#{aboutTaglines[aboutPictureNumbers.indexOf(picture)]}")
                            button.about_picture_button_mobile(class="about_picture_button_" + picture) Inquire Today
